Leave this idolatry/shirk practice and worship the one and only God through the Syariat of Muhammad Rasulullah saw as the final and seal of prophets. The Quran as the final revelation from Allah swt had allow the truth of the previous holy scriptures and overtaking, correcting and banishing the old holy scriptures [Surah al-Maidah (The Table Spread): 48]. This God is the God of Noah, the God of Abraham, the God of Moses, the God of David, the God of Jesus, peace and blessings upon them all.

Indeed, the only religion in the sight of Allah is Islam (Surah al-Imran: 19).

There shall be no compulsion in the acceptance of the religion (Surah al-Baqarah: 256).

There are consequences to our action that will determine our final destination in the hereafter death, either in Heaven or Hell.


Be careful guys.
